  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The government of Haiti plans to introduce a flour fortification program. The aim of the
      project it to inform the authorities on the most suitable iron compound for this
      fortification program. For this purpose, iron absorption from wheat flour using different
      iron compounds will be investigated.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
